data.description: Welcome home to this adorable 3BR/2BA cape cod style escape located on a quiet nearly 2-acre wooded lot. Built in 1940, this home has an abundance of charm and character while proving unique in its design, comfort, and upkeep. Enjoy an enclosed porch flowing off the kitchen, sitting on nearly 2 acres of a wooded lot. The feel of privacy and nature, yet minutes away from any city necessities. A rare find of land, charm, and the desirable Limestone Community school district. Your retreat awaits!   Newly poured concrete back patio, furnace (2011), water softener (2021), updated central air (2022) electrical, windows, stainless steel appliances, carpet, hardwood floors & laminate. Both baths & kitchen completely remodeled. The basement has ample space for additional recreational, family area, or office potential with redone trendy concrete dry locked floors and resurfaced eye-catching black loft ceilings.
